{"tid":2511342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度拒絕聯合國援助 自稱有“穩健的醫療體系”","createTime":"2021-04-30T23:54:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T03:56:01.000Z","uid":391580,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"172bbfafb47d877e27ae5e787686a019b0acece2","tid":2511342,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T23:54:25.000Z","msg":"4月30日消息：由于近日新冠病例激增疫情失控，印度各類醫療服務陷入嚴重短缺危機。在此情況下，印度卻拒絕了聯合國新冠疫情醫療援助，並自稱印度有&ldquo;穩健的系統&rdquo;來處理所需的工作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTsaomb6BK4yJrCP5iZBGj11Ko36pHwaJ8XqSv8hQduiS?filename=6RnUWTR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6RnUWTR.jpg&h=c4838e60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNpHuUpTbuXec4kmP7X41jHqGegjXHHRDT1UtaJbgCkhJ?filename=M93hadU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM93hadU.jpg&h=88dd0578&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《印度報》29日消息，聯合國秘書長古特雷斯的發言人哈克（Farhan;Haq）說，&ldquo;我們所做的其中一件事是，如果需要的話，我們能提供綜合供應鏈援助。在這一點上，我們被（印度）告知不需要這樣做，因為印度有一個相當健全的體系來處理這一問題。但我們的提議仍是有效的，我們願意以任何方式提供幫助&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n網友們評論紛紛嘲諷：什麼是&ldquo;穩健系統&rdquo;？那它什麼時候開始工作？<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdR7RDxqFgvh9BQDfRuzHTKkkhHzu8US9pDtZMRHhNPs5?filename=yfGys0F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyfGys0F.jpg&h=a2b8fa74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ62gE9DaqWuh6LYhQ3MWXQ9mMVfqCdokK6tTWwMGyfuq?filename=vZCYD7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvZCYD7r.jpg&h=03bc07f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友評論截圖<br />\n<br />\n據印度衛生部門30日發布的最新統計數據顯示，過去24小時，印度累計報告新冠確診病例386452例，再次刷新該國疫情暴發以來的紀錄，新增死亡病例3498例，連續9天單日新增超30萬例。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTJ7v6V1uTX5t698ZtXT5Cf1hUHSNFKhm4Jy75hp4DD9S?filename=8nh9LNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nh9LNx.jpg&h=a93ee245&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當地時間2021年4月28日，印度新德裏，一名婦女坐在醫院臨時的新冠肺炎護理中心內的病床上吸氧。<br />\n<br />\n以首都新德裏為中心，印度各地醫用氧氣短缺致衆多患者死亡，醫療系統陷入危機狀況。醫院和火葬場都嚴重超負荷，印度開始將工業氧氣轉化為醫療使用，甚至改造狗火葬場，用于火化新冠逝者。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVP1udxFSbhkQHyWMxdR22pxBXTTepapm3PokXpBw1xbn?filename=YRXt1k1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRXt1k1.jpg&h=d1d9aa20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關于聯合國機構的重要物資是否有望在危機中運抵印度這一問題，哈克表示：&ldquo;迄今為止我們還沒有收到援助請求，但正如我所說，如果需要我們，我們確實有人願意提供幫助。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"9c3e7495bb572c55641c96f7c1f715627069a0c6","tid":2511342,"uid":162160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:13:12.000Z","msg":"全面封鎖印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1feb9550272f1a65c9ea55ac92e6ec8e5e85a254","tid":2511342,"uid":99627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:27:04.000Z","msg":"係咪睇唔起聯合國咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9a4b2eb1fe55fe4b26f6a43e3cd027a5fa15fd","tid":2511342,"uid":381265,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:28:49.000Z","msg":"我估暗地裏聯合國提出啲不合理嘅條件"},{"pid":"1650ad62c49e4910f9748fe574c18d43878dca71","tid":2511342,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T00:39:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />識野，知道UN俾支那操控"},{"pid":"5c8a690c07d30362b2558f3b36ea22335747b7de","tid":2511342,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T01:44:08.000Z","msg":"日日新高都仲係到打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be0d5fd1886f8ed4a70451cc1dcf3597b03de6cc","tid":2511342,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T01:45:24.000Z","msg":"一比聯合蟈介入<br />\n<br />\n死得仲慘"},{"pid":"636bec72a90a435f80e174487a14c760d9905006","tid":2511342,"uid":297997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1650ad62c49e4910f9748fe574c18d43878dca71","tid":2511342,"uid